snippet.title: Click For Cash | Official Trailer 2022 - Jupitr Entertainment
snippet.description:
Get ready to click till' you're filthy rich!

Click For Cash is a idle clicker game where you click a button for cash (very self explanatory). Purchase a variety of upgrades to help you become the richest person in the universe... at least in the game.

Click For Cash is set for a September 15th, 2022 release date for Windows and Android!
